# List of State Register of Heritage Places in the Shire of Wongan-Ballidu

The State Register of Heritage Places is maintained by the Heritage Council of Western Australia. , 184 places are heritage-listed in the Shire of Wongan–Ballidu, of which five are on the State Register of Heritage Places.
List
The Western Australian State Register of Heritage Places, , lists the following five state registered places within the Shire of Wongan–Ballidu:
